detail_desc: Set with three wrapover bodysuits and three pairs of shorts in soft, organic cotton jersey. Short-sleeved bodysuits with a wrapover front and press-studs at the sides and crotch. Shorts with an elasticated waist.
Short-sleeved shirt in a patterned viscose weave with a resort collar, French front and straight-cut hem.

Double-breasted trenchcoat in sturdy cotton twill with a collar with an adjustable storm tab and a concealed hook-and-eye fastening at the front. Shoulder tabs with a decorative button, a loose yoke front and back, side pockets and two inner pockets. Adjustable belt with a buckle at the waist, and a high single back vent with a concealed fastening. Lined.
Slightly shorter jumper in a soft, fine knit with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Sun hat in cotton poplin. Width of brim 5 cm. Lined.
Scarf in a patterned cotton weave.
Cap in cotton twill with an adjustable metal fastening at the back.
Nursing poncho in a soft fine knit containing some wool. Open at one side for easier nursing access.
Fully-fashioned trainers with a high, rib-trimmed shaft and grosgrain with a text print on the back of the heels. Mesh insoles, and EVA (ethylene-vinyl acetate) and rubber soles.

Dress with a matching hairband in soft organic cotton. Sleeveless dress with buttons on the shoulders and a sewn-in bodysuit with elasticated hems and press-studs at the crotch. Hairband with a sewn-in knot at the front and covered elastic at the back of the neck.

Straight-cut jacket in grained imitation leather with a collar, zip and wind flap with concealed press-studs down the front. Dropped shoulders and long sleeves with an adjustable tab and press-stud at the cuffs. Detachable tie belt at the waist, flap chest pockets and pockets in the side seams. Lined.

Long-sleeved shirt in a cotton blend with an easy-iron finish, turn-down collar and classic front. Narrow cuffs with adjustable buttoning, a yoke and darts at the back and a rounded hem. Slim fit with narrow shoulders and a tapered waist for a fitted silhouette.
Water bottle in stainless steel with a plastic screw cap with an eyelet and round carabiner hook. Diameter 6.5 cm, height 26.5 cm (including cap).
Tights in a soft, fine-knit cotton blend with an elasticated waist.

Longer blouse in lightweight, softly draping satin with a sheen. Small, gathered stand-up collar, a V-shaped opening at the front and a yoke with a pleat at the back. Long sleeves with wide, buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.

Top in sweatshirt fabric with an inset section at the front with a print motif and a lined, drawstring hood with a wrapover front. Kangaroo pocket and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Long cardigan in a soft, fine knit containing some wool with dropped shoulders, long, ribbed sleeves and slits in the sides. No buttons.
Long cardigan in lightweight cotton sweatshirt fabric with a hood and high stand-up collar. Diagonal zip down the front, decorative seams front and back, and pockets in the side seams.
Straight-cut T-shirt in soft, printed cotton jersey with a narrow trim around the neckline.
Long-sleeved top in sweatshirt fabric with reversible sequins on the front (sizes 1½-3Y with normal sequins), and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Scarf in woven fabric with a brushed finish and fringes on the short sides. Size 40x211 cm.

Long dress in an airy crêpe weave in a narrow cut at the top with thin shoulder straps. Opening with inset lace at the front, an open back with lace sections and an adjustable hook-and-eye fastening at the back of the neck. Seam at the waist and a flared skirt with a concealed zip at the back. Lined.
Fine-knit tights with an elasticated waist.
Round-necked T-shirt in soft cotton jersey.
Scarf in a soft, patterned weave. Size 60x200 cm.
Short coat in soft pile with narrow notch lapels, concealed press-studs down the front and side pockets. Lined.
Sports tights in fast-drying functional fabric with a wide waist panel.
Bra in ribbed jersey with underwired, padded cups that shape the bust and provide good support. Adjustable shoulder straps and a hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Fully lined bikini bottoms with a low, V-shaped waist and high-cut legs.
Straight-style jumper knitted in soft cashmere with a boat neck, dropped shoulders and long, wide sleeves with close-fitting, ribbed cuffs.

All-in-one suit in a soft cotton blend with a jersey-lined hood, concealed zip down the front with a chin guard and wide, foldover ribbing at the cuffs and hems. The cotton content of the all-in-one suit is organic.
Printed top in sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend with a lined hood and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Fully lined, patterned bikini. Top with a high cut at the front, double shoulder straps and a plastic fastener at the back. Bottoms with covered elastication at the waist.
Knee-high football socks in fine-knit, fast-drying functional yarn with elastication at the top, ankle and foot for best fit.
Straight trousers in washed cotton twill with a soft brushed finish. Adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and press-stud, and front and back pockets.
5-pocket shorts in stretch denim with a zip fly and button, and raw-edge, frayed hems.
Jumper knitted in soft cashmere. Short raglan sleeves with ribbed trims and ribbing around the neckline and hem.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a round, rib-trimmed neckline and small opening with ties at the front of the hem.

KIDS EXCLUSIVE. Jumpsuit in textured, double-weave organic cotton. Wide shoulder straps, buttons at the top and an elasticated seam at the waist. Straight, ankle-length legs with sewn-in turn-ups. Lined at the top.
Flip-flops with straps in shimmering metallic imitation leather.
Oversized, straight-cut jacket in imitation leather with a collar, covered press-studs down the front, a chest pocket and patch front pockets. Lined.
Metal anklets in different designs. Adjustable length 22-25 cm.
Shorts in softly draping weave made from a silk blend in a relaxed fit with an elasticated waist and side pockets.
Leggings in soft organic cotton jersey with an elasticated waist.
Cap in cotton twill with a print motif on the front and covered elastication at the back.
Wide headband in soft, rib-knit cashmere.
Off-the-shoulder top in soft, crinkled jersey with lace details at the front and decorative ties at the top. Elastication at the top and long sleeves with elasticated cuffs.
Sunglasses with plastic and metal frames and tinted, UV-protective lenses.
Fully lined bikini bottoms with a low waist and ties at the sides.
Make-up bag in transparent, patterned plastic with a zip at the top that continues half-way down each short side. Unlined. Size 8.5x10x18 cm.

Set with a long-sleeved top and pair of leggings in jersey and shorts in lightweight sweatshirt fabric. Top with a round neck and a small opening with a button at the back of the neck. Leggings with an elasticated waist. Shorts with an elasticated waist, detachable belt in braided imitation suede, fake fly with a heart-shaped button, and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Cold shoulder top in woven fabric with narrow shoulder straps and a wide flounce at the neckline that continues down the sleeves.
Top in sweatshirt fabric with a print motif on the front, long raglan sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Treggings in stretch, denim-look jersey with an elasticated waist, fake fly, fake front pockets and real back pockets.
Sleeveless dress in printed cotton jersey with a gathered seam at the waist and flared skirt.
Long-sleeved cardigan in soft, fine-knit cotton with a round neck, buttons down the front and slits in the sides. Ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Fine-knit trainer socks in a soft cotton blend with elasticated tops.
Jacket in soft pile with a high stand-up collar, concealed zip down the front, side pockets and inner ribbing at the cuffs. Lined.
Top in soft fabric with a motif, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline and hem.
Jumper in a soft, fine knit containing some wool. Relaxed fit with gently dropped shoulders and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Fully lined, textured swimsuit with padded cups that shape the bust and provide good support. Concealed elastication under the bust and a low-cut back.
Dress in soft, fine-knit cotton with plastic beads at the top, a round neckline, short sleeves and gently flared skirt.
One-shoulder blouse in airy cotton poplin with an elasticated top and long sleeves with elastication at the cuffs.

Long dress in glittery patterned mesh with a V-neck at the front, deep V-neck at the back and concealed zip in one side. Adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps that cross, lace and fasten at the back, seam at the waist and a flare to the hem. Satin lining.
Two-strand necklace with a chunky metal chain and pearly plastic beads. Adjustable length. Trigger clasp.
Leggings in sturdy jersey made from an organic cotton blend with an elasticated waist.
Sleeveless top in soft, ribbed jersey with wrapover draping at the front and a practical inner top for easier nursing access.
Short pyjama shorts in soft satin with narrow elastication at the waist and wide lace sections at the sides.
Fully lined swimsuit with a wide flounce at the top, one wide shoulder strap and a high cut at the back.
Shorts in a cotton weave with an elasticated, drawstring waist, fake fly and fake front pockets.
Jumper in fine-knit cotton with long raglan sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Short-sleeved dress in patterned cotton jersey with a lined hood, print motif on the front, seam at the hips and gently flared skirt. Unlined.
Suede shoulder bag with a zip at the top, one outer compartment with a press-stud, one inner compartment, and an adjustable, detachable shoulder strap. Cotton lining.
T-shirts in soft, organic cotton jersey.
Briefs in organic cotton jersey with lace details, a high waist, lined gusset and full coverage at the back. Gathers in the sides for best fit over the tummy.

Trousers in airy chiffon made from recycled polyester with a high, elasticated drawstring waist and concealed pockets in the side seams. Low crotch and extra-wide, flared legs. Jersey lining at the top.
Short jumper in a soft, fine knit with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Fitted top in jersey with a lace yoke at the back, an opening with a covered button at the back of the neck and long sleeves.
Derby shoes in grained imitation leather with open lacing at the front and a decorative welt seam around the soles. Cotton canvas linings and insoles and rubber soles. Heel approx. 2 cm.

Suit trousers woven in a linen blend with a concealed hook-and-eye fastening, zip fly, diagonal side pockets and jetted back pockets with a button. Slim Fit that is close-fitting at the thighs, knees and ankles to create a fitted silhouette.
